Photo:VCGThe fourth plenary session of the 19th Central Committee of the Communist Party of China (CPC) will be held from October 28 to 31 in Beijing. The CPC Central Committee Political Bureau will report its work to the central committee, study several major issues concerning upholding and improvement of the socialism with Chinese characteristics, including modernizing the country's governance system and capacity. 
